`/newsyntax
#include <vcc.h>

_(def \integer fib(\integer x)
  _(decreases x)
{
  if (x <= 2)
    return x;
  else
    return fib(x - 1) + fib(x - 2);
})


void foo()
{
  // cannot prove that yet
  _(assert fib(3) == 3)
}
`
Verification of fib succeeded.
Verification of foo failed.
